suffered a profits fall from Pounds 2.68m to Pounds 776,000 pre-tax.
The total dividend year is being cut to 2.5p (5.75p) via a reduced final of
0.85p. Earnings per share were 1.4p (6.5p).
The second half deficit of Pounds 493,000 compared with previous profits of
Pounds 1.57m.
