<HEADLINE>
FT  09 MAR 94 / World News in Brief: Trams return to Sarajevo
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Residents in the Bosnian capital wept and cheered as trams ran in the city
for the first time since May 1992. Sarajevo is in its fourth week of a
generally successful ceasefire.
Picture, Page 2
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>BAZ  Bosnia-Hercegovina, East Europe.
